# No interactive sbt

Interactive sbt **blocks the agent** (parent and subagents). Never run it.

## Forbidden

- Any task named `console`, `consoleQuick`, or `Test/console`
- Project-scoped forms: `liga/console`, `liga/Test/console`, `*/console`
- Bare `sbt` / `sbt --client` with no task
- Watch modes: `~compile`, `~test`, etc.

```bash
# ❌ hangs
sbt --client "liga/Test/console"
sbt --client console
sbt --client "liga/console"
```

## Use instead

```bash
sbt --client "liga/compile"
sbt --client "liga/test"
sbt --client "liga/testOnly *BracketSpec*"
sbt --client fixup
sbt run   # startup only; no --client
```

Do not open the REPL to inspect types or try expressions — write/run a test.
